'''Willy Lin''' is a businessman stationed in [[Hong Kong]]. His company, Milos, handles textiles and manufacturing. He is also the head of the shippers council and one of the most prominent men in [[Hong Kong]]. He has also received an [[Order of the British Empire|MBE]] (Member of the Order of the British Empire) and is a [[Justice of Peace]].<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.hkshippers.org.hk/pdf/member_assop26-27_eng.pdf|title=Annual Review: Honorary Chairmen|publisher=Hong Kong Shippers' Council|accessdate=28 December 2010}}</ref> He has factories in [[Thailand]], [[Hong Kong]] and [[China]].

